configuration/preprocessors.md
     1â†’# Configuring Preprocessors
     3â†’Preprocessors are extensions that can modify the raw Markdown source before it gets sent to the renderer.
     4â†’
     5â†’The following preprocessors are built-in and included by default:
     6â†’
     7â†’- `links`: Expands the `{{ #playground }}`, `{{ #include }}`, and `{{ #rustdoc_include }}` handlebars
     8â†’  helpers in a chapter to include the contents of a file.
